;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black; position:relative;top:5.0pt;mso-text-raise:-5.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=81 height=21 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151126/07/38/565797f8618a31448581112.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1026&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black'&gt;的解集是&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size: 11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black'&gt;　　&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体; color:black'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:90:"2015-2016学年黑龙江省大庆市铁人中学高二上学期第一次月考数学试题";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:5;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"189046";s:7:"options";N;s:7:"content";s:2592:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;若函数&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;=loga&lt;/span&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;x3&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;ax&lt;/span&gt;）（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;＞&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a≠1&lt;/span&gt;）在区间（&lt;span lang=EN-US style='position:relative;top:11.0pt; mso-text-raise:-11.0pt'&gt;&lt;img width=28 height=35 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151201/22/32/565daf65c4c3c1448980325.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;）内单调递增，则实数&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;的取值范围是，不等式&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;2x&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;2≥m2&lt;/span&gt;﹣&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;3m&lt;/span&gt;恒成立；命题&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;q&lt;/span&gt;：存在&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Cambria Math&quot;;color:black'&gt;∈&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;，使得&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m≤ax&lt;/span&gt;成立．&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）若&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;为真命题，求&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;的取值范围；&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;）当&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;a=1&lt;/span&gt;，若&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;;color:black'&gt;∧&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体; color:black'&gt;q&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;为假，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;p∨q&lt;/span&gt;为真，求&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;的取值范围．&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:76:"2016届辽宁省沈阳二中高三上学期暑期检测数学（文）试题";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}}
